text: Daniele Giorgini and Potito Starace are the defending champions, but they decided not to participate this year. Dino Marcan and Antonio Šančić won the title, defeating César Ramírez and Miguel Ángel Reyes-Varela in the final 6–3, 6–710–12, [12–10]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Draw=== ==References== * Main Draw San Benedetto Tennis Cup - Doubles 2015 - Doubles
